  "prompt": "What are some cute names to call your boyfriend in Spanish?",
  "response": "Here are some cute names you can call your boyfriend in Spanish:\n\n1. **Cari\u00f1o** - Darling\n2. **Mi amor** - My love\n3. **Cielo** - Heaven or sky\n4. **Coraz\u00f3n** - Heart\n5. **Mi vida** - My life\n6. **Tesoro** - Treasure\n7. **Amorcito** - Little love\n8. **Bomb\u00f3n** - Sweetie (literally, a type of candy)\n9. **Mi rey** - My king\n10. **Papito** - Daddy (often used affectionately)\n\nThese terms are commonly used as expressions of affection and can add sweetness to your interactions.",
